      "rationale": "In-vitro validation experiments conducted under controlled temperature (37°C ± 0.5°C), hematocrit (35% ± 1%), and anticoagulation (heparin 1 U/mL) conditions representative of CPB clinical practice. Flow rates and rotational speeds matched CFD boundary conditions within 1.5%. Environmental conditions documented in lab notebook LN-2023-047."
