      "rationale": "Predicted normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) compared against experimentally measured values at all 5 operating points. Predictions fall within ±10% of measured values at all points; mean absolute percentage error 6.2%. Comparison metrics include NIH, relative hemolysis index (RH), and plasma-free hemoglobin accumulation rate. Statistical agreement assessed via Bland-Altman analysis confirming no systematic bias."
