      "rationale": "Validation activities performed on the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry under CPB-representative flow conditions (2–6 L/min, 2000–3500 RPM). Validation domain encompasses the intended COU operating envelope. Blood analog fluid properties (viscosity, density) matched clinical blood properties. Geometric similarity between validation and COU configurations confirmed through dimensional analysis."
